global_rules.character_restrictions: Does not use letter 'O' on standard plates - only number zero '0'

stacked_characters.position: INCLUDE 'M' as prefix (Michigan State Univ), INCLUDE 'S' as prefix (Michigan State Univ), INCLUDE smaller 'M' in MIDDLE, INCLUDE smaller 'D' in MIDDLE. OMIT 'EX POW', OMIT one 'DV' if both present.
stacked_characters.notes: INCLUDE: MSU 'M' (MI-MAA00A), MSU 'S' (MI-SAA00A), smaller 'M' (MI-105M540), smaller 'D' (MI-001D255). OMIT: 'EX POW', one 'DV' if both present. OMIT ALL branch of service or campaign names.
